    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-strung S54B32 3.2L inline-six power plant. This unit maintains excellent compression across all cylinders, with the individual throttle bodies providing the sharp throttle response these chassis are known for. The double-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced to ensure precise valve timing throughout the 8,000 RPM range. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip variable M differential. The suspension geometry remains true, and the rear subframe has been proactively inspected for structural integrity. While it bears the minor cosmetic patina of a well-enjoyed machine, its mechanical vitals and chassis dynamics are dialed in for the purist.",
